public class DeviceCVMKeyguardActivity
extends com.gemalto.mfs.mwsdk.internal.cdcvm.DeviceCVMDefaultKeyguardActivity
A class that manages the Device keyguard mechanism when CHVerificationMethod is DEVICE_KEYGUARD.

It can act also as a fallback mechanism if biometric fingerprint fails.
